  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Describe the absorption and emission of radiation in terms of atomic energy levels and energy differences</item>
<item>Use quantum numbers to estimate the energy, frequency, and wavelength of photons produced by atomic transitions in multi-electron atoms</item>
<item>Explain radiation concepts in the context of atomic fluorescence and X-rays</item>
</list></md:abstract>
